{"tid":1688654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【立即行動】強烈呼籲 消防員．各部門公務員，一齊聯署同武裝份子割蓆！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:40:09.000Z","uid":54684,"like":200,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"27a9deced2b780dd4544690070033b67685d7aea","tid":1688654,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過左今晚，做公僕既你，重忍到？</span></strong></span><br />\n依家有班人已經覺得自己係全世界，全社會既話事人，佢地大哂<br />\n無需要守任何rules，無需要跟任何程序，行使任何權力<br />\n佢地覺得<br />\n我要批評你，我就批評你，無人阻到<br />\n我要打爆你，我就打爆你，無人阻到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁重成世界？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地重可以命令你，命令所有人為佢做事<br />\n依家重隨便捉你，打你<br />\n你質疑佢，佢可以圍你，烚你<br />\n每日 武裝份子(我必須咁講，好客觀，岩唔岩？) 發布最新片段，公開講話，就係度扭曲事實，<br />\n而你，選擇忍氣吞聲？畀佢地欺負？<br />\n<br />\n消防員．各部門公務員，你地受左氣咁耐<br />\nCome on，再次聯署，同武裝份子  <strong>割蓆</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府高層係咪成日話要割蓆？<br />\n依家就係割蓆既時候！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地係街上打橫行   亂打人    因為恃住佢地gear好<br />\n但係，佢地最大弱點係心理<br />\n而你地可以打擊到佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後講多次︰<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">止暴制亂  你地有責任</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d8d555c92beb6b237cbd980ea1e1f40f9484539b","tid":1688654,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6fdbd7d6196cebe6079cd98e650c01759c8708","tid":1688654,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫