ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要有黃繼續討好佢地為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n上次集會+罷工+聯署 已經有老屎忽反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好在少部分老屎忽冇威力 影響唔到其他老前輩老師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c4323eb3052000e94e94dce9816a8637353530","tid":1688654,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"如果再搞多次聯署  逐個部門爆   一定有noise"},{"pid":"2f51a6a9e99111b79cb30b4f26ecb3467760e15b","tid":1688654,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04acea3171add893550d101e448acbde3c196a05","tid":1688654,"uid":261345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"公務員大射波"},{"pid":"81820c6be9b31ebc126b1b73d4db1e60caab273b","tid":1688654,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"再推  推畀多D公務員睇到"},{"pid":"91089bd856f71f8f1d91f2661d0a4a3716058b18","tid":1688654,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a9deced2b780dd4544690070033b67685d7aea","tid":1688654,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過左今晚，做公僕既你，重忍到？</span></strong></span><br />\n依家有班人已經覺得自己係全世界，全社會既話事人，佢地大哂<br />\n無需要守任何rules，無需要跟任何程序，行使任何權力<br />\n佢地覺得<br />\n我要批評你，我就批評你，無人阻到<br />\n我要打爆你，我就打爆你，無人阻到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁重成世界？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地重可以命令你，命令所有人為佢做事<br />\n依家重隨便捉你，打你<br />\n你質疑佢，佢可以圍你，烚你<br />\n每日 武裝份子(我必須咁講，好客觀，岩唔岩？) 發布最新片段，公開講話，就係度扭曲事實，<br />\n而你，選擇忍氣吞聲？畀佢地欺負？<br />\n<br />\n消防員．各部門公務員，你地受左氣咁耐<br />\nCome on，再次聯署，同武裝份子  <strong>割蓆</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府高層係咪成日話要割蓆？<br />\n依家就係割蓆既時候！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地係街上打橫行   亂打人    因為恃住佢地gear好<br />\n但係，佢地最大弱點係心理<br />\n而你地可以打擊到佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後講多次︰<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">止暴制亂  你地有責任</div></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"無錯 今日消防 下次可能漁農 食環"},{"pid":"2bff43de7fe476f0ed76a964e63d66ccbd52706a","tid":1688654,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">習曱甴</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">習曱甴</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">習曱甴</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">習曱甴</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">習曱甴</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">習曱甴</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zC6guCC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzC6guCC.jpg&h=bf37842c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHsn9CD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHsn9CD.jpg&h=fe8df6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/118e0Kk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F118e0Kk.jpg&h=339bfc3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwExNps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwExNps.jpg&h=41a49463&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0b6e1ee097f26085c39d0359d0e506b99c0b9a59","tid":1688654,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39adc5e8520d27e68bca281189d05662db96ee21","tid":1688654,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc80db11e7270ea8